CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 6, 2008

[Cite as 03/06/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-903.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-0034. State ex rel. Shea v. Hillcrest Ambulance Serv.

Franklin App. No. 07AP-136, 2007-Ohio-6536. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
